Yours Truly is the debut studio album by American recording artist Ariana Grande, released on August 30, 2013 in Germany and The Netherlands through Republic Records. The US release occurred on September 3, 2013. It has been preceded by the release of two singles: the US Billboard top-ten hit "The Way" featuring Mac Miller, as well as "Baby I", which peaked at number 21. A promotional single entitled "Right There" (featuring Big Sean) was also released before the rest of the album.
